metadata.name: TagsController #info tag belongs to a tag group doesn't return tag groups if tag groups aren't visible

children.name: Tag(id: integer, name: string, topic_count: integer, created_at: datetime, updated_at: datetime, pm_topic_count: integer, target_tag_id: integer)
ApplicationRequest(id: integer, date: date, req_type: integer, count: integer)

sql_query.sql:
SELECT "tags"."name" FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "tag_group_memberships" ON "tag_group_memberships"."tag_id" = "tags"."id" INNER JOIN "tag_groups" ON "tag_groups"."id" = "tag_group_memberships"."tag_group_id" WHERE (tag_groups.id NOT IN (
        SELECT tag_group_id
        FROM tag_group_permissions
        WHERE group_id = 0))
